metadata.label: Enrichments
metadata.comment: Standardizes account data by updating column names and calculating residual terms. It processes dates, maps housing purposes, and categorizes accounts into short or long-term based on residual years.

expression.expression:
CASE
WHEN From_Date = last_day(From_Date) THEN From_Date
ELSE last_day(date_sub(From_Date, 30))
END

case
when Residual_years >0 and Residual_years <1 then "Short Term"
when Residual_years >1 then "Long Term"
else "Long Term"
end
